metadata.name: Empire State of Mind
metadata.description:
On Monday Feb 6th, a devastating earthquake hit Turkey and Syria. To aid relief efforts, AzukiNYC will dedicate all proceeds of mint towards  non-profit organizations through The Giving Block. 
This artwork features the spirit of AzukiNYC community to go beyond the art and and support. We are Azuki, we are AzukiNYC. Artwork done by the talented @pipusuuu. Group commission by members of AzukiNYC.
